date=March 15, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.top-charts.com/s/sunday-best-surfaces|title=Sunday Best by Surfaces|website=Top-Charts.com|access-date=March 15, 2020}}</ref> The song peaked in the Top 40 in Australia, Canada, Norway, Ireland, New Zealand and the United Kingdom, as well as the top 100 in the United States, Switzerland, Germany and Sweden.\n\n== Live performances ==\nSurfaces made their late-night television debut when they performed the song on ''[[Late Night with Seth Meyers]]'' on March 2, 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://headlineplanet.com/home/2020/03/03/surfaces-perform-on-late-night-with-seth-meyers-first-look/|title=Surfaces Perform \"Sunday Best\" On \"Late Night With Seth Meyers\"|last=Cantor|first=Brian|date=March 3, 2020|website=Headline Planet|access-date=March 15, 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Charts ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=March 30, 2020|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n| 12\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|57|artist=Surfaces|song=Sunday Best|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 2, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders|15|artist=Surfaces|song=Sunday Best|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 4, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Wallonia|39|artist=Surfaces|song=Sunday Best|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 4, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Canada|8|artist=Surfaces|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 31, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Czechdigital|9|year=2020|week=14|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 7, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Denmark ([[Tracklisten]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitlisten.nu/default.asp?w=12&y=2020&list=t40|title=Track Top-40 Uge 12, 2020|publisher=[[Hitlisten]]|accessdate=April 1, 2020}}</ref>\n| 24\n|-\n! scope