ember 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* ''Hot Summer Medley'' 2019 06-06-2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lgbtqmusicchart.uk/2019/07/07/lgbtq-music-chart-week-28-2019/|title=LGBTQ Music Chart \u2013 Week 28 \u2013 2019|last=Chart|first=LGBTQ Music|date=2019-07-07|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190708092330/https://lgbtqmusicchart.uk/2019/07/07/lgbtq-music-chart-week-28-2019/|archive-date=2019-07-08|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.prsformusic.com/|title=PRS Tunecode 367446HR  \"Hot summer medley\"|date=3 November 2019|website=PRS for Music|access-date=3 November 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101124205/https://www.prsformusic.com/|archive-date=1 November 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/track/1wfvpdyE760R6BEb1QzCui|title=ST MUSIC LLC Repertory|website=www.spotify.com|access-date=3 November 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191103111500/https://open.spotify.com/track/1wfvpdyE760R6BEb1QzCui|archive-date=3 November 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* ''Planet Called Love'' 2019 31-07-2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lgbtqmusicchart.uk/2019/10/06/lgbtq-music-chart-week-41-2019/|title=LGBTQ Music Chart \u2013 Week 41 \u2013 2019|last=Chart|first=LGBTQ Music|date=2019-08-05|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007080630/https://lgbtqmusicchart.uk/2019/10/06/lgbtq-music-chart-week-41-2019/|archive-date=2019-10-07|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.prsformusic.com/|title=PRS Tunecode 363797LQ  \"Planet called love\"|date=3 November 2019|website=PRS for Music|access-date=3 November 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101124205/https://www.prsformusic.com/|archive-date=1 November 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/track/4ihX18emCgd7Kgd0KvibDS|title=ST MUSIC LLC Repertory|website=www.spotify.com|access-date=3 November 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191103111459/https://open.spotify.com/track/4ihX18emCgd7Kgd0KvibDS|archive-date=3 November 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* ''Universal Party (Supernatural)'' 2020 14-02-2020<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.prsformusic.com/|title=PRS Tunecode 382887GW  \"Universal Party (Supernatural)\"|date=14 February 2020|website=PRS for Music|access-date=3 November 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101124205/https://www.prsformusic.com/|archive-date=1 November 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/6x0GVYjZH9pIBFo2eKDJVT|title=ST MUSIC LLC Repertory|website=www.spotify.com|access-date=14 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lgbtqmusicchart.uk/2020/02/21/new-gay-music-outed-on-fridays-week-08-2020/|title=New Gay Music / Outed On Fridays!|website=lgbtqmusicchart.uk|access-date=24 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224123837/https://lgbtqmusicchart.uk/2020/02/21/new-gay-music-outed-on-fridays-week-08-2020/|archive-date=24 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n===Charts songs===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of charted songs, with selected chart positions, showing year released and album name\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:20em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\"| UK chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Peak position\n! scope=\"col\" | Weeks on chart\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Avalon L.A.\" \n| 2017 \n| 1<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.numberonemusic.com/charts?country_id=224&filter_action=1&genre_id=95&geo=national&query=avalon%20gravity%20noir|title=N1M EDM Chart \u2013 Week 1 \u2013 2019|last=Chart|first=N1M EDM|date=2019-01-05|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-12}}</ref>\n| 65\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''Liberation''\n|-\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Open your mind\"\n| 2019\n| 1<ref>{{Cite web|url=http:/