.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Jorg Van der Heyden \u2013 dancer, graphic designer (1996\u20132019)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* C.J. \u2013 main vocals, backing vocals, dancer (1996\u20131997)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Sofie \u2013 dancer (1996\u20131997)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Andrew Williams \u2013 main vocals, backing vocals, wind instruments, graphic designer (2016\u2013present)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://jaxsta.com/recording/04144f94-c2ee-4b7b-a644-f38f20886444/overview|title=Open Your Mind (feat. Andrew Williams)|website=www.jaxsta.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://jaxsta.com/recording/04144f94-c2ee-4b7b-a644-f38f20886444/overview|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Kenny Patrick Cogen \u2013 dancer (2016\u2013present)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Suzanne Vuegen \u2013 dancer (2016\u2013present)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|title=Gravity Noir Official Website|website=www.gravitynoir.com|access-date=1 April 2020|archive-url=https://gravitynoir.com/bandmembers|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n== Discography ==\n\n; Albums\n\n* ''The Early Years''  2016  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191061029427)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gravitynoir.com/dashboard/pages/videos_90s|title=Gravity Noir The early years|last=Gravity|first=Noir|date=2015-11-10|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-12-01}}</ref>\n* ''Handmade''  2016  (CD Baby/Indieplant/Gravity Productions UPC 0680596923527)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7BRUG7fgQfA&list=OLAK5uy_kGxBjMk__4DeDCTrnNz1qI0LTEpjXNz7M|title=Gravity Noir Handmade|last=Topic|first=YouTube|date=2016-11-30|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/artist/gravity-noir-mn0003626360|title=Gravity Noir|last=AllMusic|first=Discography|date=2016-11-30|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110093113/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/gravity-noir-mn0003626360|archive-date=2019-11-10|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* ''Liberation''  2017  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191924097662)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4kVDpT7mCM&list=OLAK5uy_mKmWl_dmyfTowUcW-qdtu4C6xsT8Y-rTY|title=Gravity Noir Liberation|last=Topic|first=YouTube|date=2017-11-09|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/artist/gravity-noir-mn0003626360|title=Gravity Noir|last=AllMusic|first=Discography|date=2016-11-30|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110093113/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/gravity-noir-mn0003626360|archive-date=2019-11-10|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* ''The Singles''  2017  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191924217718)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z7R9uaJD7oI&list=OLAK5uy_lVn0q25uaazGs0Xy-OPoLl2GXf10-E28Y|title=Gravity Noir The Singles|last=Topic|first=YouTube|date=2017-08-19|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref>\n* ''The Remixes''  2017  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191924450573)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jAhuxvdAqjY&list=OLAK5uy_kjh3K071598lu_2g-2-n_inyYhbjALtEk|title=Gravity Noir The Remixes|last=Topic|first=YouTube|date=2017-04-08|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref>\n* ''Future Days''  2020  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 192914889168)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/be/album/future-days/1489030385?l=en|title=Future Days by Gravity Noir|last=Music|first=Apple|date=2020-03-18|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-03-18}}</ref>\n\n; EPs\n\n* ''Welcome to My Gravity''  2016  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191061056942)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ascap.com/repertory#ace/search/title/welcome%20to%20my%20gravity/performer/gravity%20noir|title=ACE Repertory|website=www.ascap.com|access-date=11 November 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127100731/https://www.ascap.com/repertory#ace/search/title/welcome%20to%20my%20gravity/performer/gravity%20noir|archive-date=27 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* ''The Remix'' ''EP''  2016  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 190394642938)\n* ''Into a New World''  2017  (CD Baby/Gravity Productions UPC 191924194972)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ascap.com/repertory#ace/search/title/into%20a%20new%20world/performer/gravity%20noir|title=ACE Repertory|website=www.ascap.com|access-date=11 November 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127100731/https://www.ascap.com/repertory#ace/search/title/into%20a%20new%20world/performer/gravity%20noir|archive-date=27 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n; Singles\n\n* ''I've Got the Power'' 2011 23-04-2011<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.prsformusic.com/|